Titolo: Highway Patrol 2

Anno: 1991

Descrizione: Highway Patrol 2 is a vehicle simulation and racing game developed by Micro√Øds in 1991. In this game, the player is a police officer trying to capture runaways before they reach the border of the state. The game begins with choosing a target, each one with different rewards: the tougher the criminal, the higher the reward will be. The game is played in a first-person view, with a map and a compass to help in locating the criminal. To arrest him, players may choose to use the soft way (siren), or the hard way (shotgun).

Genere: Racing 

